title: Tomato Crop for Market for United States
notes:
Units Represent Bushels Of Approximately 53 Pounds. Some Quantities Not Marketed Are Included For The Years 1931-1935; 1938; 1940-1943; 1945-1946; 1948-1949. Source: U.S. Department Of Agriculture, Agricultural Statistics, 1942, 1950, 1951.
